01:22:12.880 --> 01:22:16.159
who are mentors for me, role models, for hard work,

01:22:16.640 --> 01:22:19.719
for questioning myself, for doing a thousand shots a day.

01:22:19.960 --> 01:22:22.157
What happens if you make a thousand calls a day?

01:22:22.722 --> 01:22:23.475
100 calls a day?

01:22:24.042 --> 01:22:26.055
Rather than one call a week?

01:22:26.782 --> 01:22:28.460
No, but it's the law of numbers at some point.

01:22:28.780 --> 01:22:32.039
So, sometimes it takes longer, but that's just part of life,

01:22:32.444 --> 01:22:33.619
and that's what I encourage you to do.

01:22:34.060 --> 01:22:38.060
So now, we're going to do an audit of the top 25 qualities for success.

01:22:38.442 --> 01:22:40.359
But before that, you need to understand a basic principle.

01:22:40.579 --> 01:22:42.300
It's that you need to change your perspective,

01:22:43.140 --> 01:22:47.380
you first have to break down your not-so-great habits,

01:22:47.983 --> 01:22:50.479
to be polite, and build new ones.

01:22:51.122 --> 01:22:52.180
So, there are two categories.

01:22:52.341 --> 01:22:55.380
So now, I'm going to share with you the 25 qualities of success.

01:22:56.481 --> 01:22:58.399
And the goal is going to be to rate yourself on these.

01:22:58.600 --> 01:23:00.819
So, some are about attitude,

01:23:01.483 --> 01:23:02.399
so, personality traits,

01:23:02.579 --> 01:23:04.380
and some are about skills,

01:23:04.622 --> 01:23:06.420
that you'll need to develop.

01:23:06.862 --> 01:23:08.159
So now, the question you might ask yourself is,

01:23:08.563 --> 01:23:10.494
is it possible to change your personality?

01:23:11.341 --> 01:23:11.404
OK.

01:23:13.242 --> 01:23:15.238
"Oh, but I'm always late!

01:23:15.882 --> 01:23:17.595
That's just how I am, you can't change!

01:23:19.520 --> 01:23:20.579
Unbearable, loser mindset.

